            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <app><note>The conjectural restoration, derived from the transcription of Amico  is that of Kirchhoff in CIG, repeated by Kaibel in IG</note></app>
                    <app loc="3"><note>Amico: ...ΑΕΥ...</note></app>
                </listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <p>Here lies [---], having lived for [--] years; they passed away on the [---] of January.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The restoration of Kirchhoff is obviously speculative, particularly in lines 3-4, but plausible, based upon the formularity of such texts, and suggesting that only a small amount is missing from the left margin of the fragment.</p>
            </div>
